casebody.data:
Stark County Bar Association v. Ross.

[Cite as Stark Cty. Bar Assn. v. Ross (1987), 34 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(D.D. No. 87-9 Decided December 16, 1987.)

On Certified Report by the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline of the Bar.

William J. Ross is publicly reprimanded. Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
